############ The following steps will be covered in this chapter ############
1) Creating simple S3 objects to simplyfy code
2) Taking advantage of generic object functions with S3 classes
3) Creating structured and formal object with the S4 system
4) simple way to package code for4 sharing and reuse
5) using devtools to host code from github
6) building a unit test suite to ensure that functions work as you intend\
7) using countinuous integration with travis to keep code tested and up to date
